7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Transition from OHSAS 18001 replace ISO 45001"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:42+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"ISO 45001 replacing OHSAS 18001: Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE who compares the current documentation listing with the new requirements to get ISO"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Transition from OHSAS 18001 replace ISO 45001"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001:2018 is the new standard for creating an Occupational Health & Safety Management System (OHSMS). OHSAS 18001:2007 standard was not maintained by the International Organization for Standardization (ISO), there is some confusion as to whether this is a replacement standard. If your organization has implemented OHSAS 18001, is it necessary for transition to ISO 45001? Yes, because ISO 45001 will replace OHSAS 18001. Learn the difference between ISO 45001 and OHSAS 18001."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"About ISO 45001:2018 standard"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 standards include many of the same requirements, as both the standards are used to create an OHSMS. Both the standards emphasize the management of Occupational Health & Safety (OH&S) hazards and legal requirements, and the involvement of top-level management , there are some new requirements in the ISO 45001:2018 standard that are included to further benefit the company in Dubai and rest of UAE. For more information on the benefits that ISO 45001 can bring, see the article benefits of ISO 45001 for your business."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The biggest changes is to organize the ISO 45001 standard to match the standard format for ISO management systems, called Annex SL, so that the structure and format match the other management systems such as ISO 9001:2015 and ISO 14001:2015 standard. For more information on the structure, see the article ISO 45001 requirements and structure."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Another change is risk involved in the OHSMS. OHSAS 18001 standard demonstrates about the risks associated with the OH&S hazards in the organization, where as ISO 45001 explains the way to manage other risks and opportunities along with controlling the OH&S hazards."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"New requirements of ISO 45001"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 certification documentation information is confusing for most of the companies in UAE. The new requirements ISO 45001 certification are basically an amalgamation and simplification of the old requirements for creating and maintaining documents and records in the OHSMS. The ISO 45001 standard clarifies that documented information refers the ISO 45001 certification management system and its processes, information created for the organization, and evidence of results achieved. The process that has been put into place for document and record control in OHSAS 18001 will meet the requirements of ISO 45001."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19"]}],"$L1a"]}]}]
