e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"Compare OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 | OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 | Wizms"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"ISO 45001 replacing OHSAS 18001: Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE who compares the current documentation listing with the new requirements to get ISO"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"OHSAS 18001 to ISO 45001, iso 18001 to 45001, iso 18001 and 45001, iso 45001 replacing ohsas 18001, compare ohsas 18001 and iso 45001, ISO 45001 replaces OHSAS 18001, iso 18001 vs 45001, comparison of ohsas 18001 and iso 45001, ohsas 18001 iso 14001"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"Compare OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 | OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 | Wizms"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"ISO 45001 replacing OHSAS 18001: Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE who compares the current documentation listing with the new requirements to get ISO"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/transition-from-ohsas-18001-to-iso-45001"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:30:42+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Compare OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 | OHSAS 18001 and ISO 45001 | Wizms"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"ISO 45001 replacing OHSAS 18001: Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE who compares the current documentation listing with the new requirements to get ISO"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L1b","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The new ISO 45001 standard also has different expectations of what documentation will require, so ensure that best ISO consultant compares the current documentation listing with the new requirements to ISO 9001:2015 and ISO 14001:2015 standard. For more information on the structure, see the article get ISO 45001 certification."}]
11:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Is there a need for transition from OHSAS 18001 to ISO 45001?"}]
12:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Both ISO and BSI have indicated that there is a three-year transition time period to change your OHSMS from OHSAS 18001:2007 to the new ISO 45001:2018 standard. This matches when ISO 9001:2008 is updated to the ISO 9001:2015 revision. Companies who have already OHSAS 18001 certified until 2021, have to upgrade their OHSMS, ISO has indicated that it will make OHSAS 18001:2007 obsolete. Any company in Dubai and UAE that is implementing a new OHSMS, should use the ISO 45001 standard as their requirements, because ISO certification bodies will stop granting certification to the OHSAS 18001 standard sooner than this 2021 deadline."}]
13:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"So, it is clear that ISO 45001 replaces OHSAS 18001. Now, for your transition, you need a great plan. Start with a gap analysis process and compare it to the requirements of the ISO 45001:2018 standard. In this gap analysis, go through every statement and determine whether ISO 45001 requirements are met or not. If some of the requirement are not met, determine what need to do to meet it, and then make that changes. But it can take some time to do. ISO 45001 Gap Analysis Tool can help to perform gap analysis."}]
14:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Start the ISO 45001 Certification Process as early as possible"}]
15:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Many companies in UAE tend to wait to make the changes in their system, but this can be problematic. Transition from OHSAS 18001 to ISO 45001 take some time to accomplish. Waiting to start the transition will only delay your conclusion, and rushing because you started late can hinder the improvements or changes."}]
16:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Thinks to Remember"}]
17:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Making improvement changes to OHSMS, so that it meets the ISO 45001 requirements does not mean that need to change ISO certificate right away. Take the time to make the changes, implementing the most important first, and get the benefits of each improvement."}]
18:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Certification in UAE is a most preferred Certification Standard by organizations in UAE from all sectors. WIZMS provides ISO Certification in UAE for all major standards such as ISO 9001, ISO 14001, ISO 27001, ISO 17025, ISO 45001 and more."}]
19:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"WIZMS is the best ISO consultant in UAE and provides ISO consulting services in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain and Fujairah. WIZMS is one of the leading ISO consultant in Dubai who offers top-class ISO consultancy services including ISO Consulting, ISO Certification, ISO Training in UAE, Gap analysis, Documentation, Implementation, and ISO certification audits in UAE."}]
